lead_paragraph: Wales's Euro 2016 victory over Belgium, officially the second-best team in football, showed again that you can have all the attacking talent in the world but if you are weak at the back you will be found out at the highest level.

headline.print_headline: Analysis-Belgium Floored by Denayer's Defensive Disaster
